      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../img/me.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;alebaffa&#34; style=&#34;width: 300px; float: left; margin-right: 20px&#34;/&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Alessandro Baffa&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color:#e80918; color: white&#34;&gt;Software Engineer&lt;/span&gt; &amp;ndash;&amp;gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.linkedin.com/in/alessandrobaffa&#34;&gt;LinkedIn&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Strong advocate of &lt;span style=&#34;background-color:#7ef7ed; color: black&#34;&gt;clean code&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;background-color:#f77ed9; color: black&#34;&gt;testing&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;background-color:#c63717; color: white&#34;&gt;quality&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;background-color:#17c629; color: white&#34;&gt;continuous learning&lt;/span&gt; and &lt;span style=&#34;background-color:#1723c6; color: white&#34;&gt;continuous improvement&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I push my projects and what I learn on &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/alebaffa&#34;&gt;Github&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I love &lt;span style=&#34;background-color:#09a8e8; color: white&#34;&gt;to organize&lt;/span&gt; learning activities and helping others to improve their skills.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I am good at &lt;span style=&#34;background-color:#e8d109; color: black&#34;&gt;motivating people&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I am a &lt;span style=&#34;background-color:#e83209; color: white&#34;&gt;photography enthusiast&lt;/span&gt; &amp;ndash;&amp;gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/alebaffa/&#34;&gt;Flickr&lt;/a&gt;. You can also find me on &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/alebaffa&#34;&gt;Twitter&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This blog contains my personal thoughts about things that I learn.&lt;/p&gt;
